column4: NSLOCTEXT("[5227960A4C23301EB4873D97C2033D77]", "0C248428481898E134BD058B991205FB", "I\'ll bring something soon. Hang on little more.")
NSLOCTEXT("[5227960A4C23301EB4873D97C2033D77]", "D6C58BF7436458F15428CA9DF3CF8D1A", "I\'m saved. Thanks so much. Sorry for the trouble.")
NSLOCTEXT("[5227960A4C23301EB4873D97C2033D77]", "594D7EEF490AB85761DAC1B02273F1EA", "I\'m {Player}, a human from another world. This is my partner, {Partner}.")
NSLOCTEXT("[5227960A4C23301EB4873D97C2033D77]", "ED285A3344FC94F9CA530496E6237583", "Looks like we have lot to talk about. I welcome you.")
